Package org.com.controller.dataimport

Klasse DataImporterController

java.lang.Object
org.com.controller.dataimport.DataImporterController
public class DataImporterController extends Object
Controller for handling data import operations in the application. Manages the import of cinematic data from CSV files, coordinates with various services for data processing, and updates the application state accordingly.
Version:
1.0
